neruniface_104uvn1665702612860.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uvn1665702612860.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uvn1665702612860.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uvn1665702612860\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Logical widget for styling the default entity widget <code class=\"ph codeph\">udefentity</code> in Form components. The properties set are applied to all entities in the application. If DefEntity is not defined, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">udefentity</code> widget is transparent and follows Windows conventions.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uvn1665702612860__topic_d144377e1_d144378e1_d144379e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvn1665702612860__p_d144380e1_d144381e1_d144382e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DefEntity</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">udefentity</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uvn1665702612860__section_mtc_vyw_wvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d307966e81\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>—semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"uvn1665702612860__table_d17516e1_d17517e1_d17518e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"uvn1665702612860__table_d17516e1_d17517e1_d17518e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"uvn1665702612860__table_d17516e1_d17517e1_d17518e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-fi